<p>
<lb n="1"/>© śrī madāha<unclear>va</unclear>mallēśvaradēvara mānya [hiṁbahi <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ] yiṁ baḍagaṇa
<lb n="2"/>26 mattaroḷage <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Oleya bēriseṭṭigavanaṁtara nāgalegaṁ samastabhū
<lb n="3" break="no"/>pālakarāmalakṣmaṇara pōlume kadarghu guḍayyaseṭṭi saldile
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ya kaṇniseṭṭiyaradhīśvaranāhavamalla bhaktisalla Upa lō
<lb n="5" break="no"/>kadābharaṇa jaṁgama liṁgapada prasādaru <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> toṟanaṟidu
<lb n="6"/>buguḍa karṇnaṁna keṟeyiṁ samakaṭṭi keḷage mattoṁmattartteṟeyi
<lb n="7" break="no"/>lladukṣiyaṁ muṁdaṟidu parikrayava koṁḍadakkarpisidaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="8"/>Ā dēvara holada sīme mūḍalu kaḷanakuppa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> teṁkalu kaḍiyakallasaripi
<lb n="9"/>paḍuvalu tuṁgabhadra baḍagalu haḷla Āṁntāpūṭa 26 mattaroḷage naḍu
<lb n="10"/>mattaṁme keṟeya keḷage <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> mattaru 1 biṭaru <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

